description: Healthcare Cost Report Information System (HCRIS) Dataset - Independent Rural Health Clinic and Freestanding Federally Qualified Health Center (HCLINIC).This data was reported on form CMS-222-92. The data in this release includes years FY2009 to present. The HCLINIC Cost Report Data contains cost and statistical data for Independent Rural Health Clinic and Freestanding Federally Qualified Health Center providers.
title: Health Clinic Cost Reports
